---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title='3D Web Experiences'
  description='Transform your web presence with immersive 3D experiences that captivate users and bring your products to life.'
>
  <div class="high-contrast-section bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700">
    <h2 class="text-slate-100">Short Description</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-200 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      I specialize in creating engaging 3D web experiences that help businesses showcase their products and services in innovative ways. Additionally, I develop 3DGS Gaussian splat scenes for spaces and objects, delivering high-fidelity visuals as a service to clients. Using cutting-edge WebGL technology and modern frameworks, I build performant and interactive 3D applications that work seamlessly across all devices.
    </p>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>

<style>
  .example-project {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .example-project h3 {
    color: theme(colors.blue.300);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .results {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
</style>
